by javiereguiluz at 2021-03-10T08:21:26Z

@parijke using GitHub CLI (https://github.com/cli/cli) you can run this command: `gh pr checkout 4230` in your local clone of EasyAdmin (and then use `ln -s ...` to change `vendor/easycorp/easyadmin-bundle/` in your Symfony project to point to your local clone).

