by javiereguiluz at 2021-03-10T10:20:12Z

This is what I do in my local apps, but adapted to your directories:

```
$ cd /home/parijke/www/my-test
$ rm -fr vendor/easycorp/easyadmin-bundle
$ ln -s /home/parijke/www/EasyAdminBundle /home/parijke/www/my-test/vendor/easycorp/easyadmin-bundle
$ rm -fr var/cache/*
```

The last cache deletion is important because the classes have changed their location, so you'll get loading errors.

